src/
├── types/index.ts           ← Every type mirrors your backend exactly
├── lib/
│   ├── api.ts               ← Full client for ALL backend endpoints
│   └── utils.ts             ← Formatters (time, severity, status, roles)
├── context/AuthContext.tsx  ← Auth state + 3 demo users (no Firebase needed for demo)
├── hooks/index.ts           ← Polling hooks: useIncidents, useIncident,
│                               useHeatmap, useStaffPresence, useDeadmanSessions
├── components/
│   ├── ui/index.tsx         ← Card, Button, Badge, Stat, Spinner, ProgressBar, etc.
│   ├── Navbar.tsx           ← Sticky nav with live incident counter + ticker
│   ├── IncidentCard.tsx     ← Severity-colored cards + compact rows
│   ├── FloorHeatmap.tsx     ← Clickable room grid (green/amber/red/gray)
│   ├── TaskList.tsx         ← Accept → Start → Complete task flow
│   ├── StaffPresence.tsx    ← Live welfare tracker with silent alerts
│   └── DeadmanWidget.tsx    ← SVG countdown ring with ping button
└── app/
    ├── page.tsx              → Login + 3 demo quick-access buttons
    ├── dashboard/page.tsx    → Command center: metrics, live ticker, simulator
    ├── dashboard/incidents/  → List with status filters
    ├── dashboard/incidents/[id]/ → Full detail: AI briefing, tasks, heatmap, reports
    ├── dashboard/staff/      → On-duty toggle + role breakdown
    ├── dashboard/drills/     → Trigger drills + history with metrics
    ├── dashboard/reports/    → AI compliance reports with timeline
    ├── sos/                  → Mobile guest SOS → dead man's switch
    └── responder/            → Public first responder portal (no auth)